                </p>
                <pb facs="0750" n="732" xml:id="pg_732"/>
                <p>5. Dept fully appreciates need for intelligent orderly planning Ital Govt but
                    wishes to emphasize highly tentative and conditional character preliminary
                    program outlined under para 3 above.</p>
                <p>6. Present plan involves early approval of target program of shipments thru Feb
                    which we are preparing to discuss with Ital Tech Del within next few days.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
